_clearProposal(uint256).details: Removes an expired proposal from the system

params._index: Index of the proposal to clear

announceResults(uint256[]).details: Announces the results of multiple proposals

params._tallyIds: Array of proposal IDs to announce

answer(uint256[],uint8[]).details: Records TOAD's answers for multiple proposals

params._answers: Array of answers corresponding to each proposal
params._tallyIds: Array of proposal IDs to answer

canVote(uint256[]).details: Checks if TOAD can vote on specified proposals

params._tallyIds: Array of proposal IDs to check

returns.results: Array of boolean values indicating if TOAD can vote on each proposal

clearProposalByIndex(uint256).details: Clears a proposal by its index

params._index: The index of the proposal to clear

clearProposalByTallyId(uint256).details: Clears a proposal by its tally ID

params._tallyId: The ID of the proposal to clear

constructor.details: Initializes the contract with the TOAD address

discoverProposals(uint256[],uint256[]).details: Discovers and registers new proposals in the system

params._tallyIds: Array of proposal IDs to register
params._votingPeriods: Array of voting period durations for each proposal

getProposal(uint256).details: Retrieves a proposal by its ID

params._tallyId: The ID of the proposal to retrieve

returns._0: The proposal data without the disablers mapping

hasVotingPower(address).details: Checks if a user has voting power either through delegation to TOAD or token balance

returns._0: bool Whether the address has voting power

isMember(address).details: Checks if an address has delegated to TOAD

returns._0: bool Whether the address has delegated to TOAD

setDisablePower(uint256[]).details: Sets the voting power for specified proposals. This will not disable TOAD's voting ability until toggle is called.

params._tallyIds: Array of proposal IDs to set disable power for

toggle(uint256[],address).details: Toggles the disable power for specified proposals. If the member has not confirmed the disable power, it will be added to the proposal. If the user is not a member, it will be removed from the proposal and the disable power will be subtracted from the proposal. If the user is the member, it will be removed from the proposal and the disable power will be subtracted from the proposal.

params._member: The address of the member to toggle disable power for
params._tallyIds: Array of proposal IDs to toggle disable power for

vote(uint256[]).details: Casts votes on proposals using stored answers

params._tallyIds: Array of proposal IDs to vote on

_clearProposal(uint256).notice: Proposal must be past its voting period to be cleared

announceResults(uint256[]).notice: Results can only be announced once per proposal

answer(uint256[],uint8[]).notice: Proposals must be within their valid block period

canVote(uint256[]).notice: This is a gas-intensive operation and should be used off-chain

clearProposalByIndex(uint256).notice: Proposal must be past its voting period to be cleared

clearProposalByTallyId(uint256).notice: Proposal must be past its voting period to be cleared

discoverProposals(uint256[],uint256[]).notice: Clears inactive proposals before registering new ones

vote(uint256[]).notice: Only TOAD can call this functionTOAD must be able to vote on the proposals (checked via canVote)
